        public static void loadFrom(java.io.File... directories)
        Loads all the routines files (.rou) from the directories specified as parameters, the routines that were parsed correctly can be found with getRoutines(). Routines are considerd equal and hence are not duplicated in the list on the base of the Routine.equals(Object) method.
